  {
    "hotel_id": "2543257",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hive-hotel_2/hotel/yilan-tw.html",
    "name": "Check inn Hive",
    "detail": "Location is fantastic. Located across the street from the front of Luodong train station (back is the bus station). Just 3mins away, super convenient. There are tourist bus that brings you around Yilan from the bus station. Hive hotel is on the right side when you face the road (with the train station behind you). Just after a bubble tea shop called MILK SHOP. Rooms are clean & nice as per pictured. Enough space to open up three 28 luggages comfortably. Love the Loccitane toiletries, snacks & drinks provided! My booking included daily bfast. Quality food & drinks provided, with 3 choices available (they don't change their menu daily tho). There are also many eateries around the area & Luodong night market is nearby (less than 10mins away). Turn right out of hotel, turn left when you see the 1st traffic light, walk on then turn right after the next traffic light you see. Use Google map to navigate. Staff are all very friendly. Highly recommend Hive! ",
